, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/288226/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ethosuximide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Ganaxolone, Vigabatrin, More', 'Paritaprevir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, Famciclovir, Voxilaprevir, Pibrentasvir, Rimantadine, Telbivudine, Entecavir, More', 1767369485);
